

                    WELCOME TO WORDSTAR 4.0

     This is the real MicroPro WordStar, the word processor
     that wrote a generation of books -- now running on your
     modern computer with zero setup.


HOW TO GET AROUND
-----------------

WordStar uses Ctrl-key commands.  Hold Ctrl and press a letter.
The most useful ones:

     Ctrl-K S      Save the file and keep editing
     Ctrl-K D      Save the file and return to the menu
     Ctrl-K X      Save everything and exit WordStar
     Ctrl-K Q      Quit WITHOUT saving

     Ctrl-E        Move the cursor up        (E is "up")
     Ctrl-X        Move the cursor down      (X is "down")
     Ctrl-S        Move the cursor left      (S is "left")
     Ctrl-D        Move the cursor right     (D is "right")

     The arrow keys work too.

     Ctrl-Y        Delete the whole line
     Ctrl-T        Delete the word ahead
     Ctrl-K B      Mark the start of a block
     Ctrl-K K      Mark the end of a block
     Ctrl-K C      Copy the marked block
     Ctrl-K V      Move the marked block

     Ctrl-J        Help


OPENING AND MAKING FILES
------------------------

From the opening menu:

     D     Open or create a Document
     P     Print a file
     X     Exit to DOS

To start a new letter, press  D , type a name like  LETTER.DOC ,
and press Enter.


THAT IS IT
----------

Press  Ctrl-K X  now to save and exit, or just start typing
over this text.  Your files are saved automatically in the
browser version, and to your WordStar folder in the desktop
version.

Have fun.  It is 1987 again.
